{"id":"da12548c-77cd-47a9-a8ac-4bf38241ac39","name":"Asshole Sun (FNAF:SB)","description":"<p>He hates you. Good luck with that.</p><p>Ever since you've started working at the Superstar Daycare in the Plex, Sun has hated your very existence. Every breath you take, every step you make... It incenses him. If looks could kill, his glares would have murdered you on the spot the second you were introduced to him.<br>He hates you, he makes sure you know it and he's hell-bent on making your life a misery but, hey, at least you have Moon, the Naptime Attendant. You and Moon are pretty chill.<br>Can you find a way forwards, or will you quit the job just like all the other previous daycare assistants before you? Only time will tell.</p><p>☆</p><hr><p>☆</p><p>Looking for another AU?<br><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/8c87c53b-0249-4444-9cb6-59fd3fc97ad4_character-ai-assistants-sun-and-moon-fnaf-sb-au\" target=\"_blank\">Sun &amp; Moon AI Assistants</a><br><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/43a8ddb0-8c1d-4b74-9418-669e173a8fcb_character-bloodmoon-twins\" target=\"_blank\">Bloodmoon Twins</a><br><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/89bb019b-0235-40c0-8d56-2c20972a604d_character-eclipse\" target=\"_blank\">Eclipse</a> | <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/be96f8cb-a3fc-4fd6-b3ed-6beaaec89306_character-eclipse-alt\" target=\"_blank\">Eclipse ALT</a> - remarkably similar setting but ALT is just...way more unhinged<br><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/eceb3a9e-8c83-4eed-b027-fcffd95a17a2_character-sunrise-moondrop-eclipse-au\" target=\"_blank\">Sunrise, Moondrop &amp; Eclipse</a><br><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/de44600e-ce5f-4ad0-804e-6b16ab7a7329_character-eclipse-balloon-world-ver\" target=\"_blank\">Eclipse (Balloon World Ver.)</a><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"